        self.x = x
        self.y = y

    dist_z = body2_position.z - body1_position.z

    return force

    for i in range(len(bodies)):
        for j in range(i + 1, len(bodies)):
            force = calculate_force(bodies[i][0], bodies[i][1], bodies[j][0], bodies[j][1])
            total_force += force
    return total_force
